'''The Brightlands''' was a [[Podracing/Legends|podracing]] track on [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]], the first of two in the [[Podracing Open]] championship. It was named after and located in the coolest region of the [[Bright Lands]], the "day side" of Ryloth.

It crossed the [[Crater Sea]] and was located near the [[Great Tusks]].

In [[24 BBY/Legends|24 BBY]], [[Mawhonic/Legends|Mawhonic]] was the track favorite.

